https://app.getguru.com/card/ioEz79XT/The-Guru-Pull-Request-Process

## Steps for testing

1. This should include a list of steps for what the reviewer should be testing
2. And also, instructions for how the reviewer can best navigate to your test cases
3. Please be as specific as possible and include any applicable/helpful screenshots/videos
4. Also include any feature flags or teams the reviewer should know about/test with

## What changes have a chance of breaking things?

- This should include an optional list of things
- That have a chance of being affected and/or breaking
- That the reviewer should go through with extra attention

pull_request.title: Guruhacks/extension fun onboarding
pull_request.body:
<!---
Pull Request Guidelines:
https://app.getguru.com/card/ioEz79XT/The-Guru-Pull-Request-Process
-->

## Steps for testing

1. This should include a list of steps for what the reviewer should be testing
2. And also, instructions for how the reviewer can best navigate to your test cases
3. Please be as specific as possible and include any applicable/helpful screenshots/videos
4. Also include any feature flags or teams the reviewer should know about/test with

## What changes have a chance of breaking things?

- This should include an optional list of things
- That have a chance of being affected and/or breaking
- That the reviewer should go through with extra attention
